## CodeGraph

This project has CodeGraph MCP (`codegraph_*` tools). Use it for structural questions (definitions, callers, call paths, impact). Use grep only for literal text.

Full guide: `docs/CODEGRAPH.md`

If `.codegraph/` is missing, offer `codegraph init -i`.
